06:56:15.479 --> 06:56:18.119
At this school, you will be learning side

06:56:18.119 --> 06:56:19.919
by side with dragons from all the other

06:56:19.919 --> 06:56:20.400
tribes.

06:56:20.459 --> 06:56:22.680
So we wanted to give you some basic

06:56:22.680 --> 06:56:24.900
information that may be useful as you get

06:56:24.900 --> 06:56:25.500
to know one another.

06:56:25.560 --> 06:56:28.680
You have been assigned to a winglet with

06:56:28.680 --> 06:56:29.759
6 other dragons.

06:56:29.819 --> 06:56:31.979
The Winglit groups are listed on the

06:56:31.979 --> 06:56:32.580
following page.

06:56:32.700 --> 06:56:34.919
Thank you for being a part of this

06:56:34.919 --> 06:56:35.159
school.

06:56:35.220 --> 06:56:38.159
You are the hope of Pyre's future.

06:56:38.220 --> 06:56:40.740
You are the dragons, who can bring

06:56:40.740 --> 06:56:42.299
lasting peace to this world.

06:56:42.360 --> 06:56:45.540
We wish you all the power of wings of

06:56:45.540 --> 06:56:45.840
fire.

